<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #333;
    }

    p {
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .otp {
      font-size: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #e0e0e0;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #aaa;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>OTP Verification</h2>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Please use the following OTP to verify your email address:</p>
    <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
    <p>If you didn't request this verification, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Thank you,</p>
    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <p style="font-weight: bold;">Team Codenox</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Codenox. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>